    "en": {
      "title": "School is 03 days a week",
      "author": "unknown",
      "body_lines": [
        "Schools will start next Monday (25th) and from that day until further notice, the Ministry of Education states that schools should be held as usual on Monday, Tuesday and Thursday only.",
        "The Ministry of Education has also advised that on Wednesdays and Fridays when schools are not held, students should be given learning activities from home or teaching should be done online."
      ],
